rows.label: qst660201_msg0001
rows.name:
You've had yourself a lot of adventures,
haven't you?

rows.label: qst660201_msg0002
rows.name:
You wouldn't mind regaling me with a
tale or two of them? I've an itching to 
compose a song on this Torigonda.

rows.label: qst660201_msg0003
rows.name: I'll make it worth your while, of course.

rows.label: qst660201_msg0102
rows.name:
I think this tale has the makings of a
fine song... Yes, indeed...

rows.label: qst660201_msg0103
rows.name:
If any other memories beg to be told, 
you know where to find me.

rows.label: qst660201_msg0202
rows.name:
You know where to find me, should you
change your mind.
